description:
This is a 25 minute workout called '25 MIN STRETCH & CORE - Full Body RECOVERY (Mobility, Flexibility Workout at home), no equipment' from the channel growingannanas.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: 25 minutes of dynamic stretching and strengthening exercises to increase your overall flexibility and improve your core strength. The perfect way to move your body even on your recovery days.

Please remember that we all are different and that you make this YOUR OWN workout... take a longer break when you need to.
